.Dd June 16, 2003
.Dt DCONS_CROM 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm dcons_crom
.Nd Configuration ROM stub for
.Xr dcons 4
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd device dcons_crom
.Cd device dcons
.Cd device firewire
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
exposes the buffer address of
.Xr dcons 4
through the Configuration ROM of
.Xr firewire 4 .
This address is supposed to be used by
.Xr dconschat 8 .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr dcons 4 ,
.Xr firewire 4 ,
.Xr fwohci 4 ,
.Xr dconschat 8 ,
.Xr fwcontrol 8
.Sh AUTHORS
.An Hidetoshi Shimokawa Aq Mt simokawa@FreeBSD.org
.Sh BUGS
If you load
.Pa dcons_crom.ko
manually after the system is booted, you may
have to initiate a bus reset using
.Dq Nm fwcontrol Fl r
to update the Configuration ROM.
